OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will have a dry, sunny
OL,6,Fand frosty start. Cloud will build
OL,7,Fnorth through the morning with
OL,8,Fscattered showers following in the
OL,9,Fafternoon, with the chance some will
OL,10,Fbe heavy and thundery with hail.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny remaining showers will
OL,13,Fclear from the east during the
OL,14,Fevening. After a brief dry spell,
OL,15,Fcloud with outbreaks of rain will
OL,16,Fspread north from midnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FThe day will be cloudy with
OL,19,Fbands of rain, passing northeast from
OL,20,Fthe early morning. Some of this rain
OL,21,Fwill be heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
